Security-sensitive surfaces require `security-agent` review before finalization. See [.cursor/docs/orchestration-routing.md](.cursor/docs/orchestration-routing.md) for context.

Enforce:
- Include security findings in specialist summary.
- Do not finalize with unresolved high-severity security findings.
